sellerCard.description: Hi, Toseef khan is here. I have been working as a Senior WordPress Website Developer for over 5 years. Having a firm grip on HTML, PHP, CSS helps me to tailor a WordPress website design and functionalities according to the client's needs. I am known for building stunning and captivating websites for both businesses and individuals. I would love to help you with your desire website project. I'm a hard-working and dedicated person. Feel free to contact me, Thanks!

description.content:
Hello and welcome to my Gig!


Hello there, My name is Toseef khan, a Senior Web Developer in website development 24/7.


Why choose me?


I have experience with a large range of projects in Wordpress, including but not limited to a business website, blog, e-commerce, agency, directory listing, job portal, real estate and many more. I work with a focus on Standard, Aesthetics, and Professionalism to deliver the right product for your business.


What's I will Provide


Client satisfaction


  • Highly professional and responsive Wordpress site for all devices
  • Unique design of site
  • SEO and Mobile friendly structure
  • Speed optimized
  • Elementor and other Page Builder support
  • Customized design
  • E-commerce with various payment integrations
  • Premium Design
  • FREE Premium images and graphics
  • Secured and user-friendly admin panel
  • Social media integration
  • Live chat integration
  • Mailchimp or other mailing lists integrations
  • Content upload
  • Excellent Support for My Client



Guarantee


  1. Fully secured 
  2. Fast loading pages for better conversion and navigability
  3. Fully responsive
  4. Delivery on time


Feel free to contact with me!


Place Order Now and enjoy!!!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What I need first before we proceed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: First, you will have to purchase a domain & hosting. Feel free to discuss if you haven't purchased yet, I will guide. I will also need your company logo(optional) & name of the pages for website e.g. Home, About Us, Services, Contact Us. You'll have to provide me content (text, image) for the pages.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Wil you upload website on our hosting to make it live?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you will have to provide me your credential.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide free customer support after making website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide free lifetime support to all my clients.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do your provide revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide multiple revisions within the scope of the project time. Your 100% satisfaction is our first priority.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can i edit website content after website completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can also very easily edit the whole website. I will provide you a video tutorial about the changes, which you can easily manage in the future.

reviews.comment: I recently hired Toseef and he's definitely a very talented designer on Fiverr since he made my website, and I couldn't be happier with the results! From start to finish, he was professional, attentive to my needs, and incredibly creative. He took my vision and turned it into a stunning, user-friendly site that perfectly represents my brand. Communication was seamless, and he delivered everything on time. I highly recommend him to anyone looking for top-notch web design services. Five stars all the way!

I’ll definitely be working with him again. Highly recommend!
